Sen. Elizabeth Warren is demanding info from the CEO of a private equity lobbying group about the group's efforts on coronavirus relief legislation.

Warren wants comms with the Treasury Department and White House officials ⁠— including Jared Kushner. https://t.co/V1tz3XYyqd
